commentAnnotations.text: Discussion with the AbbVie TA MD may be needed prior to unblinding and crossover to verify that criteria for unequivocal PD are met.
Locally advanced breast cancer must not be primarily amenable to surgical resection or radiation with curative intent.
Subjects with BRCA variants of uncertain significance or polymorphisms in BRCA1 or BRCA2 will not be eligible for the study.
